
kar.yt server recipe

kar.yt domain registry: 101domain.com
DNS service provider: dyndns.com
GitHub repository: https://github.com/rickseeger/karyt.git
AWS config: Ubuntu Server 14.04 64-bit, t2.micro (free tier)

Software
$ sudo apt-get update
$ sudo apt-get install git emacs mysql-server python-pip python-mysql.connector
$ sudo pip-install bottle

Config
- Extract code base to ~ubuntu, web root is then: /home/ubuntu/karyt/www
- Place db password in protected directory: /home/ubuntu/auth/.credentials.db
- Configure root crontab to start bottle server on reboot
